{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "75EWQF7LRYJ5FS6FIWWA4EQEJZXAE4EB",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "501013520",
    "title": "思い出クッキング",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "すみません、店員さん。\r\nそちらの大福豆と、新鮮なミルクを――",
            "enText": "Excuse me, waiter. Daifuku beans from there \nand fresh milk―",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -6395822458335904735
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -7568363369965861741
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7692283292801915740,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店員",
            "enName": "Shop Assistant",
            "jpText": "おっ、お嬢ちゃん！　うちの大福豆に\r\n目をつけるなんて、なかなかやるね～！",
            "enText": "Oh, girl! You've got a good eye for our \ndaifuku beans!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -8906356055577360826
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 1252521032417899769
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6872910403394442299,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "ええ。こちらで非常に質のいい商品を\r\n取り扱っていると聞きましたので。",
            "enText": "Yes. I heard they have very good quality \nproducts here.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "そんなに好物なんだ？",
                    "enText": "You like it that much?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 8687539117115972545
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 5766569324113470146
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6343375436344698715,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "あら、トレーナーさん！　好物というか……\r\n『おばあ様のお汁粉』のために必要なんです。",
            "enText": "Oh my, my trainer! I need it for my favorite \nfood or…… \"Grandma's Soup\".",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": 5905546762318525064
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -6932082207142200312
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4481466080647675140,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "幼い頃、風邪で寝込んだ日に、\r\nよくおばあ様が作ってくれた真っ白なお汁粉。",
            "enText": "When I was a child, my grandmother used to \nmake pure white oshiruko (soup stock) for me \non days when I was sick in bed with a cold.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -2497375518660521087
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": 3224661131515011886
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2759541722082392736,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "目を閉じれば思い出せる、優しい温かみ――\r\nあの味を、自分でも再現してみたくて。",
            "enText": "I wanted to recreate the gentle warmth that I \ncan remember when I close my eyes.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "俺も食べてみたいな",
                    "enText": "I'd like to try it too.",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "私も食べてみたいな",
                    "enText": "I'd like to try it too.",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": -5931393696466413289
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 5268065251309994616
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8434733558054561640,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "えっ？　ト、トレーナーさんがですか！？",
            "enText": "What? You are a trainer?",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 57,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -8993089558580044476
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": 527486126833433097
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8368858674891502408,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "構いませんが、その……えっと、うぅん……。",
            "enText": "I don't mind, but that…… umm, ……",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "だめだった……？",
                    "enText": "It didn't work. ……?",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -4507223075699875589
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -7039440646752409482
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1546024916036935735,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "い、いえっ！　そんなことはありません。",
            "enText": "No, no, no! That's not true.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 57,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": 3317690816800582956
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": 1730382493450650827
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1162837293536586194,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "メジロ家の味を知ってもらうこの貴重な機会。\r\n腕によりをかけて、ご馳走いたします……！",
            "enText": "This is a rare opportunity for people to get \nto know the Mejiro family. We will put our \nskills to the test and serve you ……!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -2436990191567381099
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 4339081470469418916
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4621147501444148064,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "カフェテリアのキッチンも借りられました。\r\n準備は万全。さあ――",
            "enText": "We were also able to borrow the cafeteria \nkitchen. Everything is ready. Let's go―",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "まずどうするんだ？",
                    "enText": "What are you going to do first?",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "まずどうするの？",
                    "enText": "What do you do first?",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -567484903061672736
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 4131529559890018071
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -640609924835102780,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "す、少し待ってください！\r\nええっと、確かおばあ様の教えでは――",
            "enText": "Wait a minute! Well, I'm pretty sure my \ngrandmother taught me…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 98,
                    "pathId": 2889236150481624389
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -8148236606461924611
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -8195872677906825253
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1368990211223493339,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "そう！　豆！　まずは豆を煮込むんですの！\r\n完璧に思い出しましたわ……！",
            "enText": "Yes! Beans! First you have to cook the beans! \nI just remembered perfectly: ……!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 6754586748509969696
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": 6739795212405180666
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -5434792197242726675
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3571226355793547226,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "…………。",
            "enText": "…………",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 2677383473183263574
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -6052020730160508427
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6008884919473710493,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "……あ、あの。トレーナーさん。\r\n質問なのですが――",
            "enText": "…… Oh, um. Trainer. I have a question―",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": -3731676140869730726
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -4774053825048782340
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8028061856688207849,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "“煮込む”とは……どうすればいいんですの？",
            "enText": "What does \"stew\" mean? ……",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "えっ",
                    "enText": "What's up?",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": -6813683123099616371
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 9064146604318955517
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8548533897764145243,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "い、いえっ！　あのですね！\r\nこれは、その……うぅ……！",
            "enText": "No, no, no! You know what? It's that…… ugh ……!",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": 8400250634371651995
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": 6159678655277539835
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8090407606849936988,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "……はぁ。すみません、白状いたします。\r\n私、料理はまだまだ修行中の身でして――",
            "enText": "…… Huh. Sorry, I must confess. I'm still \nlearning how to cook.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": -7172328402452943204
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -4706452392954714968
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2970773951703342143,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "思い出のあの味を、\r\nうまく再現できる自信がないのです。",
            "enText": "I am not confident that I can successfully \nrecreate the taste of the food I remember.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それなら手伝うよ",
                    "enText": "Then I'll help you.",
                    "nextBlock": 20
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": -4677237831340089323
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -7375400683311463324
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1596315012303565843,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "本当ですかっ？　ご馳走すると言った手前、\r\n申し訳ないのですが……お願いいたします！",
            "enText": "Are you sure? I'm sorry, I know I said I'd \ntreat you, but please ……!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 47,
                    "pathId": 4104408783261698314
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 2829715233647866247
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8228874613069791977,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――まず、“煮込む”とは\r\nどういうことかについての説明を行った。",
            "enText": "―First, she explained what \nshe meant by \"stewing.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": 7228978884811617966
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": 7586170094237958713
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4276924066387948980,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "――なるほど、完璧に理解いたしました。\r\n弱火でコトコト、ですね。お任せください！",
            "enText": "―I see, I understand perfectly. Low heat and \nslow cooking, right? Leave it to me!",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 3044699967814440015
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 144,
                    "pathId": -4795397190404500200
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3847468114118643560,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "…………ところで。\r\n弱火というのは一体どのくらいの火力で？",
            "enText": "……… By the way. What exactly is low heat?",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 31,
                    "pathId": -3339026030046369459
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 905775561929080137
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -168271036830785281,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "こうして、慣れない料理に\r\nメジロマックイーンは悪戦苦闘しつつも――",
            "enText": "And so, while struggling with \nthe unfamiliarity of cooking, \nthe white meat McQueen…",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 5795977536702871340
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": 1077895421799492974
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5606323703416403983,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "完成です！　このミルクの芳しい香り……\r\nふふっ、幼い頃の記憶と同じですわ！",
            "enText": "It's done! The aromatic smell of \nthis milk…… phew, it's just like \nI remember it from my childhood!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "頑張ったな",
                    "enText": "Good job.",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "頑張ったね",
                    "enText": "Good job.",
                    "nextBlock": 26
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -5151556290764193742
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -1277943636098557318
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5427155023184439570,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "ふふっ。ええ、もちろん。\r\nおばあ様の味を再現するためですもの。",
            "enText": "Phew. Yes, of course. It's to recreate my \ngrandmother's taste.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 57,
                    "pathId": -4748045048367828663
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -1721736764542194724
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4160734997431322552,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "それに……トレーナーさんの\r\n協力があったからこそ、ですわ。",
            "enText": "Plus, I had the help of my…… trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 8131602969858821690
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": -8350149562408323773
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9065925023563081248,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "なので、トレーナーさんからひと口どうぞ。\r\n感謝のしるしです。さ、温かいうちに。",
            "enText": "So please take a bite from your trainer. \nIt's a token of our appreciation. \nNow, while it's still warm.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ゆっくり一緒に食べよう",
                    "enText": "Let's eat together slowly.",
                    "nextBlock": 29
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "一気に飲み干す",
                    "enText": "drink the whole cup in one gulp",
                    "nextBlock": 34
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 4936544474126808311
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 2086223759891600560
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3342970528045321174,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "……おばあ様にも、\r\n昔似たようなことを言われましたわ。",
            "enText": "…… My grandmother told me something similar a \nlong time ago.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 33,
                    "pathId": 1486585825460930508
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -7882274151994304275
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6612511420671941825,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "『一緒に食べてたら風邪も平気でしょう』と。\r\n実際、その時は病気の辛さを忘れられました。",
            "enText": "If we ate together, we wouldn't have to worry \nabout catching a cold. In fact, I was able to \nforget the pain of my illness at that time.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -7391972162367375576
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 8160796866665447043
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1773020146899693121,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "苦しい病気が楽しい出来事になってしまう――\r\nそれもふまえて、思い出の味なんです。",
            "enText": "A painful illness becomes a pleasant event - \nit's a taste of memories, too.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "一緒に新しい“思い出”を作ろう",
                    "enText": "Let's make new \"memories\" together!",
                    "nextBlock": 32
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -957011331945846171
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -7201920491860882550
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1668898658454598522,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "ええ、今度はトレーナーさんと一緒に。\r\nそれでは――いただきます！",
            "enText": "Yes, this time with the trainer. \nWell then ― Bon appétit!",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 32,
                    "pathId": 5660431851745089353
                },
